Solon Names Walter Bickel as Chief Restructuring Officer

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-10-05T09:27:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/solon-names-walter-bickel-as-chief-restructuring-officer.html
Solon SE (SOO1) ’s Supervisory Board
appointed Walter Bickel as the company’s chief restructuring
officer effective immediately. Management board members Martin
Detje and Andreas Amelang are leaving the company by mutual
consent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
